Woodland Park is a neighborhood conveniently located on a peninsula halfway between San Francisco and San Jose.
This community offers something for everyone with options including studios, one-, two-, and three-bedroom apartment homes, duplexes and single-family homes.
The community is within walking distance to Downtown Palo Alto shopping, parks, and a weekly Farmer's Market.
Easy access to highway 101 and the Dumbarton Bridge makes it ideal to navigate through Silicon Valley to employers such as Facebook, Tesla, Stanford, Google, and more.
